downloadTitle: Organizational Data in Microsoft 365 template - without skills
downloadDescription: Excel file template to support manual data uploads in Organizational Data in Microsoft 365
detailsSection: Use this template to prepare your organizational data before using the Organizational Data in Microsoft 365 feature in Microsoft Admin Center to upload organizational to support scenarios with Microsoft 365 applications, Viva Suite and copilot
systemRequirementsSection: The feature is available using the browser. Use excel to open the template and use any text editor to edit the CSV file.
installInstructionSection:
Select the Download button to start the download.
The download should start automatically. If prompted, select Save or Save this program to disk.
Select Open file or find the file on your device and open it.
